'''AFD China Intellectual Property Law Office''' (in Chinese 北京安信方达知识产权代理有限公司) is a privately owned IP law firm based in Beijing, China, with a client-supporting team in Maryland, U.S.A. The firm tops the volume statistics of the annual filings of Chinese invention patent applications, [[Patent Cooperation Treaty]] (PCT) international applications and overseas patent applications for domestic clients.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=list&tid=50 |title=AFD China - Introduction}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.managingip.com/Surveys.html |title=PCT Survey by Managing IP Magazine}}</ref> It provides the full range of prosecution services, and shines brightest in national phase and PCT applications.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.iam-media.com/patent1000/rankings/Detail.aspx?g=e87ccc6b-fee6-428a-a638-e2433652760c#Firms__prosecution |title=IAM Patent 1000 recommendation}}</ref>
== History == AFD China was founded in 2002 by patent attorney Xia Zheng.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=list&tid=51 |title=AFD China - Values}}</ref>
As of 2016, AFD China has about 250 employees, including 69 patent attorneys, 25 apprentice patent attorneys, 37 patent engineers, 3 trademark attorneys, 7 trademark agents, and 5 attorneys-at-law.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=list&tid=102 |title=AFD China - Professionals}}</ref>
In addition to serving as AFD China’s lead attorney and president, Zheng serves as a director of the All-China Patent Attorneys Association, a standing director of the Beijing Patent Attorneys Association and a director of the Beijing Intellectual Property Association. She is a National IP Talent named by the [[State Intellectual Property Office]] of China in 2016, an IP Star by Managing Intellectual Property since 2015, and was honored for her significant contributions to the Chinese patent and IP industries by the State Intellectual Property Office of China in 2010.<ref>{{cite web|url= http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=read&did=1194 |title=Xia Zheng}}</ref>
==Honors and awards== AFD China is consistently recommended as a top Chinese patent and trademark law firm by [[Managing IP magazine|''Managing IP'' magazine]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ipstars.com/firms/afd-china-intellectual-property-law-office/f-2285 |title=IP Stars by Managing IP magazine}}</ref> IAM Patent 1000,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iam-media.com/patent1000/rankings/Detail.aspx?g=e87ccc6b-fee6-428a-a638-e2433652760c#Firms__prosecution |title=Recommended firm by IAM Patent 1000}}</ref> Asia IP,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asiaiplaw.com/article/10/2378/ |title=Recommended firm by Asia IP}}</ref> and Legal 500.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.legal500.com/c/china/intellectual-property |title=Other recommended firm by Legal 500}}</ref> The firm is also recognized by the local IP Office, IP attorneys association and other organizations from time to time.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bjpaa.org/uploads/soft/161227/1-16122G00922.pdf |title=Beijing Patent Attorneys Association selected AFD China as one of the Beijing Excellent Patent Firms in 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bjpaa.org/uploads/soft/161230/1-161230150343.pdf |title=AFD China is accredited as an AAAA-level Patent Firm by the Beijing Patent Attorneys Association}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=read&did=2709 |title=AFD China won the title of Four-Star Patent Agency in the Comprehensive Quality Evaluation for Chinese Patent Industry organized by the China Intellectual Property News Magazine}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=read&did=2702 |title=AFD China selected into the "Good List of Beijing Business Service Industry for the Year of 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bjipo.gov.cn/zwxx/zwgg/201508/t20150807_34476.html |title=Beijing IP Office selected AFD China into the Brand Fostering Program}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://bjpaa.org/a/tongzhigonggao/2013/1204/6199.html |title=Beijing Patent Attorneys Association selected AFD China as one of the Beijing Excellent Patent Firms in 2013}}</ref> Its patent litigation case was promulgated as one of the 2014 Exemplary IPR Protection Case by the Beijing Higher Court.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afdip.com/index.php?ac=article&at=read&did=2470 |title=AFD China’s Patent Administrative Case Selected as Exemplary IPR Case of 2014}}</ref>
